description: Dominic had a membership to ButtMachineBoys years ago. He says it was the only site he'd ever paid to visit. He jumps at the chance when he hears BMB is relaunching in 2009. Dominic is like a kid in a candy store when he's in the machine room. For the Machine Challenge, he chooses the Crystal Palace and the Dragon. As we all know, we need to warm up before using the machines. Dominic goes deep with the dildo nightstick and he's ready to go. He starts standing with the Crystal Palace. The machine spins at top speed but that doesn't faze him. Will he fulfill his fantasy by being a BMB star and survive the Dragon?
title: Machine Challenge: Dominic Pacifico
